<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1867-02-28T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1867-02-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="464" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d464">
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Extract.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <head><persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Hovey</persName></head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">No. 43.]</seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>,</placeName>
                                <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-02-28"><hi rend="italic">February</hi> 28, 1867</date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Sir :</hi> Referring to your despatch No. 41, and
                            the reply of this department of the 26th of last December, I enclose for
                            your information a copy of a circular<note n="*" xml:id="d464fn1">For
                                enclosure see circular from the department of January 17, 1867, page
                                451, vol. I.</note> letter which has been addressed to some of the
                            ministers and consuls of the United States.</p>
                        <p rend="center">* * * * * * * *</p>
                        <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                        </closer>
                        <postscript>
                            <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Alvin P. Hovey</hi>, Esq., <hi rend="italic">&amp;c., &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi></p>
                        </postscript>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>